{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 18,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 437.14,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.972,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they did worship the Lord,",
      "verse": "18:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 3.152,
      "end": 4.963,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did go forth with me;",
      "verse": "18:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 5.143,
      "end": 8.765,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we did work timbers of curious workmanship.",
      "verse": "18:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 8.945,
      "end": 11.313,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord did show me from time to time",
      "verse": "18:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 11.493,
      "end": 15.069,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after what manner I should work the timbers of the ship.",
      "verse": "18:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 15.749,
      "end": 18.257,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now I, Nephi, did not work the timbers",
      "verse": "18:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 18.437,
      "end": 21.131,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after the manner which was learned by men,",
      "verse": "18:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 21.311,
      "end": 24.562,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "neither did I build the ship after the manner of men;",
      "verse": "18:2",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 24.742,
      "end": 29.154,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but I did build it after the manner which the Lord had shown unto me;",
      "verse": "18:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 29.334,
      "end": 32.771,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, it was not after the manner of men.",
      "verse": "18:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 33.451,
      "end": 36.423,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, did go into the mount oft,",
      "verse": "18:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 36.603,
      "end": 38.925,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I did pray oft unto the Lord;",
      "verse": "18:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 39.105,
      "end": 41.938,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore the Lord showed unto me great things.",
      "verse": "18:3",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 42.618,
      "end": 45.822,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that after I had finished the ship,",
      "verse": "18:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 46.002,
      "end": 48.463,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the word of the Lord,",
      "verse": "18:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 48.643,
      "end": 51.244,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my brethren beheld that it was good,",
      "verse": "18:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 51.424,
      "end": 54.861,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that the workmanship thereof was exceedingly fine;",
      "verse": "18:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 55.041,
      "end": 58.292,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they did humble themselves again before the Lord.",
      "verse": "18:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 58.972,
      "end": 62.919,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that the voice of the Lord came unto my father,",
      "verse": "18:5",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 63.099,
      "end": 65.607,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we should arise and go down into the ship.",
      "verse": "18:5",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 66.287,
      "end": 68.609,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that on the morrow,",
      "verse": "18:6",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 68.789,
      "end": 71.157,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "after we had prepared all things,",
      "verse": "18:6",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 71.337,
      "end": 74.216,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "much fruits and meat from the wilderness,",
      "verse": "18:6",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 74.396,
      "end": 76.161,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and honey in abundance,",
      "verse": "18:6",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 76.341,
      "end": 80.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and provisions according to that which the Lord had commanded us,",
      "verse": "18:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 80.329,
      "end": 84.23,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we did go down into the ship, with all our loading and our seeds,",
      "verse": "18:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 84.41,
      "end": 86.964,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and whatsoever thing we had brought with us,",
      "verse": "18:6",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 87.144,
      "end": 89.141,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "every one according to his age;",
      "verse": "18:6",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 89.321,
      "end": 93.826,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, we did all go down into the ship, with our wives and our children.",
      "verse": "18:6",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 94.506,
      "end": 98.082,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now, my father had begat two sons in the wilderness;",
      "verse": "18:7",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 98.262,
      "end": 101.652,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the elder was called Jacob and the younger Joseph.",
      "verse": "18:7",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 102.332,
      "end": 105.954,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass after we had all gone down into the ship,",
      "verse": "18:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 106.134,
      "end": 111.753,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and had taken with us our provisions and things which had been commanded us,",
      "verse": "18:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 111.933,
      "end": 113.976,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we did put forth into the sea",
      "verse": "18:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 114.156,
      "end": 118.15,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and were driven forth before the wind towards the promised land.",
      "verse": "18:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 118.83,
      "end": 123.52,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after we had been driven forth before the wind for the space of many days,",
      "verse": "18:9",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 123.7,
      "end": 128.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, my brethren and the sons of Ishmael and also their wives",
      "verse": "18:9",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 128.478,
      "end": 130.614,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "began to make themselves merry,",
      "verse": "18:9",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 130.794,
      "end": 134.091,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that they began to dance, and to sing,",
      "verse": "18:9",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 134.271,
      "end": 136.361,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to speak with much rudeness,",
      "verse": "18:9",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 136.541,
      "end": 138.77,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even that they did forget",
      "verse": "18:9",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 138.95,
      "end": 141.644,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "by what power they had been brought thither;",
      "verse": "18:9",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 141.824,
      "end": 145.075,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, they were lifted up unto exceeding rudeness.",
      "verse": "18:9",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 145.755,
      "end": 148.634,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, began to fear exceedingly",
      "verse": "18:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 148.814,
      "end": 151.229,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "lest the Lord should be angry with us,",
      "verse": "18:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 151.409,
      "end": 153.963,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and smite us because of our iniquity,",
      "verse": "18:10",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 154.143,
      "end": 157.162,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that we should be swallowed up in the depths of the sea;",
      "verse": "18:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 157.342,
      "end": 162.032,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, I, Nephi, began to speak to them with much soberness;",
      "verse": "18:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 162.212,
      "end": 164.673,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but behold they were angry with me, saying:",
      "verse": "18:10",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 164.853,
      "end": 168.8,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "We will not that our younger brother shall be a ruler over us.",
      "verse": "18:10",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 169.48,
      "end": 174.496,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that Laman and Lemuel did take me and bind me with cords,",
      "verse": "18:11",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 174.676,
      "end": 176.952,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they did treat me with much harshness;",
      "verse": "18:11",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 177.132,
      "end": 179.64,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless, the Lord did suffer it",
      "verse": "18:11",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 179.82,
      "end": 181.91,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he might show forth his power,",
      "verse": "18:11",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 182.09,
      "end": 184.458,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the fulfilling of his word",
      "verse": "18:11",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 184.638,
      "end": 187.099,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he had spoken concerning the wicked.",
      "verse": "18:11",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 187.779,
      "end": 190.937,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that after they had bound me",
      "verse": "18:12",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 191.117,
      "end": 193.346,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that I could not move,",
      "verse": "18:12",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 193.526,
      "end": 197.566,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the compass, which had been prepared of the Lord, did cease to work.",
      "verse": "18:12",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 198.246,
      "end": 201.59,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, they knew not whither they should steer the ship,",
      "verse": "18:13",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 201.77,
      "end": 204.371,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that there arose a great storm,",
      "verse": "18:13",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 204.551,
      "end": 206.919,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, a great and terrible tempest,",
      "verse": "18:13",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 207.099,
      "end": 211.975,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we were driven back upon the waters for the space of three days;",
      "verse": "18:13",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 212.155,
      "end": 215.127,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they began to be frightened exceedingly",
      "verse": "18:13",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 215.307,
      "end": 217.722,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "lest they should be drowned in the sea;",
      "verse": "18:13",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 217.902,
      "end": 220.131,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "nevertheless they did not loose me.",
      "verse": "18:13",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 220.811,
      "end": 224.015,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And on the fourth day, which we had been driven back,",
      "verse": "18:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 224.195,
      "end": 226.61,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the tempest began to be exceedingly sore.",
      "verse": "18:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 227.29,
      "end": 231.888,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we were about to be swallowed up in the depths of the sea.",
      "verse": "18:15",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 232.068,
      "end": 234.436,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after we had been driven back",
      "verse": "18:15",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 234.616,
      "end": 237.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon the waters for the space of four days,",
      "verse": "18:15",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 237.629,
      "end": 241.948,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my brethren began to see that the judgments of God were upon them,",
      "verse": "18:15",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 242.128,
      "end": 244.078,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that they must perish",
      "verse": "18:15",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 244.258,
      "end": 247.509,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save that they should repent of their iniquities;",
      "verse": "18:15",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 247.689,
      "end": 249.454,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they came unto me,",
      "verse": "18:15",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 249.634,
      "end": 252.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and loosed the bands which were upon my wrists,",
      "verse": "18:15",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 252.647,
      "end": 255.015,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and behold they had swollen exceedingly;",
      "verse": "18:15",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 255.195,
      "end": 258.121,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also mine ankles were much swollen,",
      "verse": "18:15",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 258.301,
      "end": 260.484,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and great was the soreness thereof.",
      "verse": "18:15",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 261.164,
      "end": 263.811,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nevertheless, I did look unto my God,",
      "verse": "18:16",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 263.991,
      "end": 266.592,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I did praise him all the day long;",
      "verse": "18:16",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 266.772,
      "end": 270.487,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I did not murmur against the Lord because of mine afflictions.",
      "verse": "18:16",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 271.167,
      "end": 274.371,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now my father, Lehi, had said many things unto them,",
      "verse": "18:17",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 274.551,
      "end": 277.105,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also unto the sons of Ishmael;",
      "verse": "18:17",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 277.285,
      "end": 280.443,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but, behold, they did breathe out much threatenings",
      "verse": "18:17",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 280.623,
      "end": 283.038,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "against anyone that should speak for me;",
      "verse": "18:17",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 283.218,
      "end": 285.819,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and my parents being stricken in years,",
      "verse": "18:17",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 285.999,
      "end": 290.968,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and having suffered much grief because of their children, they were brought down,",
      "verse": "18:17",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 291.148,
      "end": 293.424,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even upon their sick-beds.",
      "verse": "18:17",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 294.104,
      "end": 296.333,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Because of their grief and much sorrow,",
      "verse": "18:18",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 296.513,
      "end": 298.789,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the iniquity of my brethren,",
      "verse": "18:18",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 298.969,
      "end": 303.427,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they were brought near even to be carried out of this time to meet their God;",
      "verse": "18:18",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 303.607,
      "end": 308.251,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, their grey hairs were about to be brought down to lie low in the dust;",
      "verse": "18:18",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 308.431,
      "end": 313.261,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even they were near to be cast with sorrow into a watery grave.",
      "verse": "18:18",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 313.941,
      "end": 316.542,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And Jacob and Joseph also, being young,",
      "verse": "18:19",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 316.722,
      "end": 319.833,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having need of much nourishment, were grieved",
      "verse": "18:19",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 320.013,
      "end": 322.521,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the afflictions of their mother;",
      "verse": "18:19",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 322.701,
      "end": 325.58,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my wife with her tears and prayers,",
      "verse": "18:19",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 325.76,
      "end": 327.153,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also my children,",
      "verse": "18:19",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 327.333,
      "end": 331.095,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "did not soften the hearts of my brethren that they would loose me.",
      "verse": "18:19",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 331.775,
      "end": 334.933,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there was nothing save it were the power of God,",
      "verse": "18:20",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 335.113,
      "end": 339.478,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which threatened them with destruction, could soften their hearts;",
      "verse": "18:20",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 339.658,
      "end": 341.33,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, when they saw",
      "verse": "18:20",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 341.51,
      "end": 345.922,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they were about to be swallowed up in the depths of the sea",
      "verse": "18:20",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 346.102,
      "end": 348.935,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they repented of the thing which they had done,",
      "verse": "18:20",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 349.115,
      "end": 351.065,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "insomuch that they loosed me.",
      "verse": "18:20",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 351.745,
      "end": 356.714,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass after they had loosed me, behold, I took the compass,",
      "verse": "18:21",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 356.894,
      "end": 359.402,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it did work whither I desired it.",
      "verse": "18:21",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 359.582,
      "end": 362.554,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I prayed unto the Lord;",
      "verse": "18:21",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 362.734,
      "end": 364.545,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and after I had prayed",
      "verse": "18:21",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 364.725,
      "end": 366.397,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the winds did cease,",
      "verse": "18:21",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 366.577,
      "end": 368.342,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the storm did cease,",
      "verse": "18:21",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 368.522,
      "end": 370.194,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there was a great calm.",
      "verse": "18:21",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 370.874,
      "end": 374.589,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that I, Nephi, did guide the ship,",
      "verse": "18:22",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 374.769,
      "end": 375.93,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we sailed again",
      "verse": "18:22",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 376.11,
      "end": 377.921,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "towards the promised land.",
      "verse": "18:22",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 378.601,
      "end": 382.781,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that after we had sailed for the space of many days",
      "verse": "18:23",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 382.961,
      "end": 385.376,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "we did arrive at the promised land;",
      "verse": "18:23",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 385.556,
      "end": 387.785,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we went forth upon the land,",
      "verse": "18:23",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 387.965,
      "end": 389.776,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and did pitch our tents;",
      "verse": "18:23",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 389.956,
      "end": 392.046,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we did call it the promised land.",
      "verse": "18:23",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 392.726,
      "end": 396.07,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we did begin to till the earth,",
      "verse": "18:24",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 396.25,
      "end": 398.293,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and we began to plant seeds;",
      "verse": "18:24",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 398.473,
      "end": 401.399,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, we did put all our seeds into the earth,",
      "verse": "18:24",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 401.579,
      "end": 404.505,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which we had brought from the land of Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "18:24",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 404.685,
      "end": 407.471,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that they did grow exceedingly;",
      "verse": "18:24",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 407.651,
      "end": 409.834,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, we were blessed in abundance.",
      "verse": "18:24",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 410.514,
      "end": 414.183,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it came to pass that we did find upon the land of promise,",
      "verse": "18:25",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 414.363,
      "end": 416.871,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "as we journeyed in the wilderness,",
      "verse": "18:25",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 417.051,
      "end": 422.067,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that there were beasts in the forests of every kind, both the cow and the ox,",
      "verse": "18:25",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 422.247,
      "end": 424.151,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the ass and the horse,",
      "verse": "18:25",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 424.331,
      "end": 426.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the goat and the wild goat,",
      "verse": "18:25",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 426.647,
      "end": 428.969,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all manner of wild animals,",
      "verse": "18:25",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 429.149,
      "end": 431.517,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were for the use of men.",
      "verse": "18:25",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 431.697,
      "end": 436.48,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And we did find all manner of ore, both of gold, and of silver, and of copper.",
      "verse": "18:25",
      "lineIndex": 141
    }
  ]
}